@startuml
title Money Movement: Card to Merchant Account

[*] --> Authorized : Customer initiates payment
note right of Authorized
  Funds are "blocked" in 
  Customer's (Issuer) account.
end note

Authorized --> Captured : Merchant confirms transaction
note right of Captured
  Transaction is batched for 
  clearing with the Acquirer.
end note

state "Clearing & Settlement" as Clearing {
  [*] --> Interchange : Issuer sends funds to Acquirer
  Interchange --> FeeDeduction : MSF (1%, 2%, or 3%) calculated
  FeeDeduction --> NetFundsReady : Acquirer prepares final payout
}

Captured --> Clearing : Batch processed by Network

Clearing --> Disbursed : Payout triggered to Merchant

Disbursed --> Credited : Funds hit Merchant's BFI account

Credited --> [*] : Transaction Finalized

@enduml